{"about_the_game":"Pokaban is a puzzle game where you push cards around to make poker hands. There are marked positions that correlate to a poker hand on the screen. Once enough cards are added to a hand it will be compared with the dealer's hand. If all of your hands beat the dealer then you win the match!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">How to Play</h2><br>Push cards:<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/push_card.gif?t=1667315837\" /><br><br>When pushed into a slot the card is added to a hand<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/slots.gif?t=1667315837\" /><br><br>Once a hand is completed it will be compared with the dealer<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/slot.gif?t=1667315837\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">You cannot <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/x.png?t=1667315837\" /></h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/x.png?t=1667315837\" /> Push more than one card<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/push_fail.gif?t=1667315837\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/x.png?t=1667315837\" /> Pull cards<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/pull_card.gif?t=1667315837\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Wild</h2><br>Wild cards can take the place of any other card. It makes creating poker hands more challenging. Like other cards you can place wild cards into marked positions to add to your hand.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/wild_card.gif?t=1667315837\" /><br><br>Positions on the game board can be marked as wild. Placing a card there will turn all cards sharing the rank and suit into wild cards. Be careful though this will affect the dealer' cards as well.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/wild_slot.gif?t=1667315837\" /><br><br>These modifiers affect the dealer's cards as well so use them carefully.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/wild_mod.gif?t=1667315837\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Suit Swap</h2><br>Placing a card onto a position marked with another suit will swap the suits of both cards.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/suit_swap.gif?t=1667315837\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hand</h2><br>Add cards to your hand<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/sleeve_card.gif?t=1667315837\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/sleeve_slot.gif?t=1667315837\" /><br><br>Throw cards from your hand<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/throw.gif?t=1667315837\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Additional features<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Create and share custom levels with friends and strangers.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/editor.gif?t=1667315837\" /><br></li><li> Unlimited undo/redo movement.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/history.gif?t=1667315837\" /><br></li><li> Fully configurable keyboard/gamepad mapping<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/settings.gif?t=1667315837\" /><br></li><li> 60+ hand-made levels<br></li><li> Relaunch right where you left off<br></li><li> Stars track progress and show achievement<br></li><li> Unobtrusive hint system<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1937170/extras/hint.gif?t=1667315837\" /></li></ul></h2>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Make 10 Pairs","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1937170/c1ecd8eb3889ea2285554a511dfa8a644224d24e.jpg"},{"name":"Make 10 High Cards","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1937170/114912c26e566a7c9366b4ebdfcfc08f80d3a88e.jpg"},{"name":"Make 10 Two Pairs","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1937170/1adf2b589100fba6983ab37ef85a12eda72c8747.jpg"},{"name":"Make 10 Three of a Kinds","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1937170/2add227a00e25ad8d63eaeb18093d4603331090c.jpg"},{"name":"Make 10 Straights","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1937170/11ff3bb75e122a6f3cfd9c60da8e204e8282eab2.jpg"},{"name":"Make 10 flushes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1937170/171b78d7534cf734111e963858903886d027ff24.jpg"},{"name":"Make 10 full houses","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1937170/ab96fe5953399c9e48de281bf3eeeaac9b724244.jpg"},{"name":"Make 10 fours of a kinds","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1937170/994e4a9b0b7b411dc8a4df63956905e5e29b869d.jpg"},{"name":"Make 10 Straight Flushes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1937170/cc15a34d8ab210cbaababa4c9a71b8da0bf439a8.jpg"},{"name":"Make 10 Royal Flushes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommun